reviewText: I didn't like this video at all. it was less chit chat vs most other Mark Shuey videos but all the move are in slow motion no real time "street speed" examples, the punch defense examples are all in really slow motion with telegraphed punches, the production quality is awful it has elevator music dubbed in and they never actually do any takedowns all the example stop short of a throw I understand some throws with a cane are dangerous to attempted but this is 100% theory.
